    <section class="card">
      <h2>Lyrics</h2>
      <div class="lyrics">
        <p>
          …<strong>Watching Jesus TV</strong> captivates my heart and mind,<br>
          His broadcasts meant to lead me to be <strong>possessed by Christ;</strong><br>
          turning, I keep turning to <strong>a channel deep inside me</strong><br>
          where a repeating notion comes and says, <strong>“Jesus is the Way, Jesus is the Way.”</strong>
        </p>

        <p>
          …Watching, I keep waiting, still <strong>anticipating</strong> God<br>
          will ever show up to become <strong>the fated One;</strong><br>
          turning, I keep turning to a channel deep inside me<br>
          where that same notion comes and says, “Jesus is the Way.”
        </p>

        <p>
          …<strong>Throughout all my life I saw you</strong> in each scene you sent my way;<br>
          though I didn’t know it was you, <strong><em>I later heard you say,<br>
          “I never go away, I always stay.”</em></strong>
        </p>

        <p>
          …Jesus is the Way, Jesus is the Way.
        </p>

        <p>
          …Watching every motion in this Jesus-guided play<br>
          haunts me with the notion it’s all going to go one way;<br>
          turning, I keep turning to a channel deep inside me<br>
          where the repeating notion comes to me and says, “Jesus is the Way.”
        </p>

        <p>
          My God, take my breath away—my God, Jesus is the Way—my God, take my breath away.
        </p>
